---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout active="none" description="What AnyPlaybook is for." locale="en" path="/about/" title="About | AnyPlaybook">
  <article class="section card page-prose">
    <h1>About AnyPlaybook</h1>
    <p class="sub">A static Astro template for bilingual tutorial sites and product playbooks.</p>
    <h2>What this template includes</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Home page with a 5-step Quick Start path</li>
      <li>Learn, Templates, Resources, and Troubleshoot sections</li>
      <li>Explicit locale routing for static deployment</li>
      <li>Template-ready site config, content schema, and theme tokens</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>How downstream sites should use it</h2>
    <p>Fork the repository, change brand config, replace sample content, and keep the route structure stable.</p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
